# Thermo-nuclear review — five-slice sweep

You are reviewing the cumulative changes of the last
{{.WindowSize}} green slices on the project. The
thermo-nuclear-code-quality-review skill (loaded via --skill) is the
review playbook; apply it strictly. Your goal is to find structural
debt that has accumulated as slices stacked on top of each other —
debt no single slice's quality check would have flagged.

